EndNote Tagged format files (.enw)
.TP
.I exports/endnote_xml/
EndNote XML files
.TP
.I exports/xml/
Generic XML files

.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.lixplore_cache.json
Cache file for search results (7-day retention)
.TP
.I ./exports/
Directory containing all exported files, organized by format

.SH ENVIRONMENT
